description: The amazing team at the Made in Taiwan trailer is serving up beautiful and tasty Taiwanese cuisine, all made with love. You’re sure to savor their scrumptious selection of authentic dishes, like the Taiwanese Train Bento (savory minced pork over white rice, braised chicken leg, steamed mixed veggies, pickled cabbage, braised hard-boiled egg), or the Pork Belly Burger (slow-braised pork belly with their homemade blend of herbs & spices, on a soft white bun, and topped with pickled mustard greens, crushed peanuts, and cilantro), Cold Sesame Noodle (delicious cold noodles with cucumbers & carrots, and mixed with house-made sesame dressing, and topped with toasted sesame seeds), just to name a few. For all this and much more, make your way to Made in Taiwan!
name: Made In Taiwan Food Trailer
